                    "text": "On a failure, the target is also grabbed . On a critical failure, the target is restrained instead of grabbed. A target that is grabbed or restrained by the  *anesthetizing jaws* is attached to the weapon by the linked chain. Until the creature Escapes the jaws, it cannot move more than 250 feet from the  *anesthetizing jaws* . The Escape DC is 32.",
